\section Welcome!

Hello! This is an online guide to calculus. Calculus studies functions, limits,
rates of change, infinite sums, areas under curves, etc.
\_comment Привет! Это онлайн-учебник по математическому анализу — науке, изучающей
    функции, пределы, скорости роста, бесконечные суммы, площади под кривыми. 

Calculus is traditionally the first or one of the first branches of higher mathematics taught.
Everyone needs it - linguists, chemists, physicists, political scientists, and, of course, mathematicians themselves.
